sub_title: Student at RUG || Deputy Editor at Lelygaan Magazine || Volunteer Teacher at English Academy for Newcomers
summary:
Currently working towards attaining my bachelors in English Language and Culture, I am constantly on the look out for opportunities and projects that involve writing, editing, design and teaching. I have chosen to specialize particularly in modern literature and hone in on the intersectionality that exists between literature, culture and politics. 

I am also part of different projects, the English Academy for Newcomers and Lelygaan Magazine, where I hope to develop teaching and leadership skills, alongside writing and creative work.
